author: Mark Evans
reviewBody: Not Verified |  A totally stress-free experience as sampled on a return charter flight from the Tampa Bay area. Just eight departure gates, but ample seating and a friendly bar/cafe. No TSA hassle either. A good gateway to Biloxi, the Mississippi Gulf Coast and even Mobile AL. Close to I-10.
